<p>La Boiselle Camp<br/>Revielle 6.30am fall in 7am. Fed mules, then breakfast next parade 9am. Went out mounted with wagon to cart ammunition, 3 hrs. ride before we arr. at dump. Wheel came off so returned to camp as we could only fix it temporally, arr. aback 6.30pm. Passed Pozieres or what was left of it. (only a few tree stumps Passed about 6 tanks and 2 aeroplanes lying near the road. All destroyed. Allotted to the 4th Section 2nd D.A.C.<br/>"B" Echelon<br/>(Bde Sub)Right Section</p>
